{"tid":1444694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成立民間自衛隊","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:42:44.000Z","uid":27561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43918e7c5485a11f9309133d02003f613ca372bf","tid":1444694,"uid":27561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"由721 元朗一役開始，大家都知鄉黑合作，無差別攻擊。<br />\n今日福建幫來香港為獨立起義作熱身，以證其勇武。無差別打人，震懾香港警察，且有同胞冒認香港警察之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n將來局勢必有趨向動武之勢，我建議各勇武巴打組織成來，除了在前線，還肩負負責遊行兄弟姊妹的安全。免於他們受到鄉黑的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>還有，當勇武兄弟姊妹被人捉時，真是不好散，拉他回來。一個都不能少，守望相助</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只是提供一個方向。"},{"pid":"e9e7dbec704497cf207c0349f56b65ba2f4bfe75","tid":1444694,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=27&amp;v=23VioHPfSMc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D27%26v%3D23VioHPfSMc&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=987016c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=27&amp;v=23VioHPfSMc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/TKvXeRQo5jzNTQsNDG/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FTKvXeRQo5jzNTQsNDG%2Fgiphy.gif&h=29519775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n義士英勇救人 , 另一位義士執起跌低左既警棍打速龍, 大家一定要識救人同埋還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bad033be637a54ae122ed47bfef71e7a958ab88","tid":1444694,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"首先針對保皇黨議員辦事處 <br />\n<br />\n一日一個<br />\n<br />\n一來養精蓄銳<br />\n<br />\n二來比市民知道保皇做左幾多陰質野<br />\n<br />\n三來對準政權<br />\n<br />\n唔好再撚狗/比狗撚"},{"pid":"70f7d4ff2104773b120c483c2e5f4f0e9c734919","tid":1444694,"uid":27561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"兄弟姐妹千萬不好害怕，被捕的兄弟下場將會很慘。<br />\n他們為了我們上站於最前，勇退鄉黑，難度我們